data.description: Welcome HOME! This lovely townhome, 2 bedroom 2.5 bathroom townhouse located in Providence Place, a gated community in South Fulton. For convenience and hosting purposes there is a half bathroom on the main level of the home! This home has been renovated beautifully. If that wasn't enough, this home offers a back private space (great for gatherings) easily accessible from the kitchen. This area is easily accessible to the highways, making you 10 minutes from the worldCOs busiest airport and 20 minutes from Camp Creek Marketplace Shopping Center and more! Townhome living doesnt get any better than this!
